Title: Megamind | FULL Trailer US (2010)
Comment:
Until I saw this movie, I thought it was about Metroman turning to the dark side and Megamind taking his place as a hero. I didn't realize it was about [SPOILER ALTERT] Metroman quitting the hero game, Megamind becoming bored with victory, a new villain arising and Megamind becoming the new hero [END SPOILER]
Come to think of it, this movie came out around the same time that Mark Waid's comic series "Irredeemable" and "Incorruptible", the former focusing on a superhero suddenly beginning to slaughter the population of earth, and the latter following said hero's super-villain nemesis turning to the good side. I very well might have confused "Megamind" and "Irredemable" while reading side-by-side reviews of them, or something (I was only about 12 when all this happened).
